# ── Backend API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set ONE of the following for Claude:

# Standard API key (uses x-api-key header)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# Claude setup token / OAuth (auto-detected by sk-ant-oat01- prefix)
# Uses Bearer auth + billing attribution for Sonnet/Opus access
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-oat01-...

# OpenAI API key
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
